→ { "token": "1|abc123...", "user": {...} } ✓

POST /api/v1/logout (with Bearer token)
→ { "message": "Logged out successfully" } ✓

GET /api/v1/products (with old token after logout)
→ 401 Unauthenticated ✓`,
    },
    tip: "Use currentAccessToken()->delete() not tokens()->delete() — logs out only current device, not all devices.",
    project: null,
